1.	Introduction
To comply with those requirements in the Common Reporting Standard (CRS), released by Organization of Economic Cooperation and Development (OECD), related form signed date and US Tax reference, etc are focused.  Our bank is required to determine whether the account holder is US person for tax purposes and reporting to IRS annually.  To keep those checking result after account opening process for audit and US reporting purpose, additional FATCA related fields is added to CIF system for on boarding (new account opening) on or after 1 July 2014.

1.1	Objective

Ensure CIF system can achieve the requirements for CRS for new on boarding customers after  Jan 2017.

1.2	Scope

The CRS Enhancement implementations for new on boarding customers on or after 1 January 2017 will enhance the CIF system as:
1.	Maintain Person Information (CIFMC10)
2.	Customer Particular Maintenance (BR) (CIFMC12)
3.	Customer Particulars (Person) (CIFCC01)
4.	Daily Transactions Log Report (CIF001)
5.	Daily Transactions Log (By Name) Report (CIF001_1)
6.	CIF Branch Input Transactions (Unposted) Report (CIF001_3)
7.	CIF Branch Input Transactions (Deleted) Report (CIF001_4)
8.	Daily Transactions Log (Investment A/C) Report (CIF001_7)
9.	FATCA Exceptional Report – Daily (CIF360E)
10.	FATCA Exception Report – Monthly (CIF360EM)

1.3	Audience
The target audiences of this document are the users from RBMD, ZPMD, MCIS, RDIV, and the technical users from IDEP-HS.
1.4	Assumptions
	Only changes described in this specification will be implemented



 
2.	Function Descriptions
2.1	Summary on Online System Changes
2.1.1	Create New Customer – Person

Add FATCA related fields for on-boarding new individual customer.

Program ID	Description	System Modification
CIFMC10	Maintain Person Information		Add FATCA related fields
	Change “MOBILE NO.” to “HK MOBILE NO.”
	Add “OVERSEAS MOBILE NO.”

2.1.2	Create New Customer – Person by Branch

Add FATCA related fields for on-boarding new individual customer.

Program ID	Description	System Modification
CIFMC12	Maintain Person Info (Branch)		Add FATCA related fields
	Change “MOBILE NO.” to “HK MOBILE NO.”
	Add “OVERSEAS MOBILE NO.”

2.1.3	Enquire Customer Particulars – Person

Add FATCA related fields for individual customer.

Program ID	Description	System Modification
CIFCC01	Customer Particulars (Person)		Add FATCA related fields
	Change “MOBILE NO.” to “HK MOBILE NO.”
	Add “OVERSEAS MOBILE NO.”

 
2.2	Summary on Batch System Changes
2.2.1	Daily Transaction Log Reports

Add FATCA related fields.

Program ID	Description	System Modification
CIF001	Daily Transactions Log		Add FATCA related fields
	Change “MOBILE PHONE NO” to “HK MOBILE NO”
	Add “OVERSEAS MOBILE NO”
CIF001_1	Daily Transactions Log (By Name)		Add FATCA related fields
	Change “MOBILE PHONE NO” to “HK MOBILE NO”
	Add “OVERSEAS MOBILE NO”
CIF001_3	CIF Branch Input Transactions (Unposted)		Add FATCA related fields
	Change “MOBILE PHONE NO” to “HK MOBILE NO”
	Add “OVERSEAS MOBILE NO”
CIF001_4	CIF Branch Input Transactions (Deleted)		Add FATCA related fields
	Change “MOBILE PHONE NO” to “HK MOBILE NO”
	Add “OVERSEAS MOBILE NO”
CIF001_7	Daily Transactions Log (Investment A/C)		Add FATCA related fields
	Change “MOBILE PHONE NO” to “HK MOBILE NO”
	Add “OVERSEAS MOBILE NO”

2.2.2	FATCA Exceptional Report

Add FATCA related fields.

Program ID	Description	System Modification
CIF360E	FATCA Exceptional Report – Daily		New daily report for exceptional input of FATCA information
CIF360EM	FATA Exceptional Report – Monthly		New monthly report for exceptional input of FATCA information


 
