OFF. TEL NO.	I	O	Office Telephone Number	9(4)-9(4)-9(20)	
HK MOBILE NO.	I	O	HK Mobile Number	9(20)	
OVERSEAS MOBILE	I	O	Overseas Mobile Number

Logic:
1.	Country code and Phone no. are mandatory
2.	If country code = “1”, area code is mandatory otherwise optional	9(4)-9(4)-9(20)	
