FATCA TYPE	I	O	FATCA Type:
1.	NFP
2.	W8P
3.	W9P
4.	EXP
5.	NCP

Help menu for item selection.

Logic:
1.	Mandatory for new customer on or after 1-Jul-2014 with deposit a/c (current / savings a/c), MSG no., or SIG no.
2.	Optional for customer without deposit a/c (current / savings a/c), MSG no., and SIG no.
3.	Optional for pre-existing customer.  Not allow to change from non-blank value to blank.	X(3)	
FATCA TYPE DESCRIPTION	O		FATCA Type Description:
NFP: Non-FATCA Person
W8P: W8 Non-US Person
W9P: W9 US Person
EXP: Management Approved
NCP: Non-Consenting Person	X(25)	
