1.	A: W-8BEN
2.	B: W-8ECI
3.	C: W-8IMY
4.	D: W-4

Help menu for item selection.

Logic:
1.	Mandatory if FATCA Type = W8P
2.	Optional if FATCA Type = NFP or NCP
3.	Not applicable for other FATCA Type	X(1)	W-8BEN
WITHHOLDING TAX EXEMPT FORM TYPE DESCRIPTION	O		Exempt Form Type Description	X(20)	
WITHHOLDING TAX EXEMPT FORM SIGN DATE	I	O	Withholding Tax Exempt Form Sign Date

Logic:
1.	Mandatory if ”Withholding Tax Exempt Form Type” has value
2.	Not applicable for other cases
MMM/DD/YYYY	
W9 FORM SSN	I	O	W9 Form SSN

Logic:
1.	Mandatory if FATCA Type = W9P
2.	Not applicable for other FATCA Type	9(3)-9(2)-9(4)	
W9 FORM SIGN DATE	I	O	W9 Form Sign Date

Logic:
1.	Mandatory if FATCA Type = W9P
2.	Not applicable for other FATCA Type	MMM/DD/YYYY	
W9 REPORTING EXEMPTION	I	O	W9 Reporting Exemption
1.	Y – Exemption
2.	N – Not exemption

Logic:
1.	Mandatory if FATCA Type = W9P
2.	Not applicable for other FATCA Type	X(1)	
W9 REPORTING EXEMPTION CODE	I	O	W9 Report Exemption Code

Logic:
1.	Mandatory if W9 Reporting Exemption = Y
2.	Not applicable for other cases	X(2)	
CONSENT SIGN DATE	I	O	Consent Form Sign Date

Logic:
1.	Mandatory if FATCA Type = W9P
2.	Not applicable for other FATCA Type	MMM/DD/YYYY	
APPROVAL REMARK	I	O	Approval Remark

Logic:
1.	Mandatory if FATCA Type = EXP
2.	Not applicable for other FATCA Type	X(120)	

3.1.4	Special Handling
•	FATCA Type for all existing customers will be Blank.
•	Withholding Tax Exemption Form Expiry Date will be calculated and stored (if necessary) when transaction posted.  The date will be set to the last day of the third succeeding calendar year.



 
