4.6	FATCA Exceptional Report (Daily) – CIF360E
4.6.1	Purpose
Retrieve the exceptional input of FATCA information inputted as of report generation date.

4.6.2	Field Descriptions

#	Field Name	Size / Format	Remarks
1	BRN/DEPT	X(4)	e.g. BCCBA, X256
2	DESCRIPTION	X(40)	Description
Repeat for each branch/department
3	CUSTOMER ID	9(8)	Customer ID
4	ACCOUNT NO	X(20)	Account No.
5	FATCA TYPE	X(3)	e.g. NFP
6	EXCEPTIONAL REASON / APPROVAL REMARK	X(90)	Exception Reason / Approval Remark

Exceptional Reason:
1.	Authorized signer with U.S. country code
2.	U.S. country code in correspondence address
3.	U.S. country code in home address
4.	U.S. home phone no
5.	U.S. mobile phone no
6.	U.S. office phone no
7.	U.S. nationality
8.	FATCA Type: W8P with U.S. nationality
9.	FATCA Type: NCP
Branch Trailer Section
7	TOTAL NUMBER OF CUSTOMERS	9(10)	
8	REVIEWED BY	X(17)	

4.6.3	Selection Criteria
	Customer created on report generation date
	Change of customer’s particulars on report generation date
	Change of (add/change/delete) account owner on report generation date
	Change of (add/change) account address on report generation date
	Change of (add/change/delete) authorized signer on report generation date
	FATCA Type = NFP
	Account Holder address (home or accounts) country code = US or US Territories;
	Authorized Signer address (home or accounts) country code = US or US Territories;
	Account Holder nationality = US; or
	Account Holder Telephone no. (Home, Office, or Overseas Mobile) included US country code & area code
	FATCA Type = W8P
	Account Holder nationality = US
	FATCA Type = EXP
	FATCA Type = NCP
	Exclude all customer without FATCA Type
	Exceptional Reason:
	Authorized signer with U.S. country code:
	FATCA Type = NFP
	Has authorized signer (relation type = ‘26’) with address (Home / Account) country code = US
	U.S. country code in correspondence address
	FATCA Type = NFP
	Account address country code = US
	U.S. country code in home address
	FATCA Type = NFP
	Home address country code = US
	U.S. home phone no
	FATCA Type = NFP
	Home phone no. is US telephone no.
	U.S. mobile phone no
	FATCA Type = NFP
	Overseas mobile is US telephone no.
	U.S. office phone no
	FATCA Type = NFP
	Office phone no. is US telephone no.
	U.S. nationality
	FATCA Type = NFP
	Nationality = US
	FATCA Type: W8P with U.S. nationality
	FATCA Type = W8P
	Nationality = US
	FATCA Type: NCP
	FATCA Type = NCP
	Approval Remark
	FATCA Type = EXP

